column1: Kata Robata////The two rolls we ordered: California Roll & Crazy Roll. The California roll was slightly better than the Crazy
column2: but I've definitely had a lot better. And the seaweed paper used to roll the Crazy roll might have been my off point
column3: or maybe it was the gross looking tuna inside of it - Whatever it was
column4: I did not like it. Next time
column5: I'd definitely order one of the specialty rolls.
